{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5578b553ef","title":"毛泽东在《人民日报》发表《关于胡风反党集团的第二批材料》的编者按语稿中加写的两段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"be5c30c4d9","index":0,"year":1955,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"5578b553ef"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fa38cfbac7","type":"title","text":"毛泽东在《人民日报》发表《关于胡风反党集团的第二批材料》的编者按语稿中加写的两段话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5578b553ef"},{"id":"0e45cedf0d","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5578b553ef"},{"id":"db89f99e93","type":"paragraph","text":"有些同情胡风或者口头上反对胡风但内心是同情胡风的人们在说，那些材料大都是解放以前的，不能据此定罪。那末，好吧，现在请看第二批材料。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5578b553ef"},{"id":"3150754edc","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5578b553ef"},{"id":"56eb407231","type":"paragraph","text":"反革命的胡风分子同其他公开的或暗藏的反革命分子一样，他们是把希望寄托在反革命政权的复辟和人民革命政权的倒台的。他们认为，这就是他们要“等待”的“时机”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5578b553ef"},{"id":"43ed4622cb","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：一九五五年五月二十四日《人民日报》。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5578b553ef"}],"page":{"id":"be610102b7","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5578b553ef","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}